Selectimus (Beta)

Change of standart selects in browser.

Для работы необходима библиотека ScrollBarJS (добавлена в плагин).
Существует несколько версий:

1. Плагин jQuery
Selectimus (Beta)

Change of standart selects in browser.


For working you need to use ScrollBarJS library (just has been added to plugin).

There are two versions: 

1. jQuery plugin
2. JavaScript library 


1. 

Init - $.selectimus(select_data [, styles] [, settings]);

select_data - jQuery object or hash, which looks like:
    {
        0: document.getElementById(id),
	1: document.getElementsByTagName(name)[0],
	...
    }


styles - Hash which includes styles. Styles apply to container in which substisution select is created. If nothing styles was transfered, would apply default styles.

	background:      'white',
	display:         'block',
	border:          '1px solid #e5e5e5',
	'border-radius': '5px',
	margin:          '3px 0',
	position:        'relative',
	overflow:        'visible'

settings - Addition options to adjust design of substisution select:
	width:  factor [1 .. 10]  - add to width of subselect 5*factor pixels
	height: factor [1 .. 10]  - add to height of subselect 5*factor pixels
	rows:   number [2 .. 20]  - set rows' quantity into subselect


Если есть какие-либо предложения, пожелания, найденные баги - пишите :)

